Fworld-news%2Feach-cigarette-in-canada-to-come-with-health-warning-label-4260940%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feach-cigarette-in-canada-to-come-with-health-warning-label-4260940%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feach-cigarette-in-canada-to-come-with-health-warning-label-4260940%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta%20Is%20Blocking%20News%20On%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%20In%20Canada.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMeta%20on%20Wednesday%20started%20blocking%20Canadians'%20access%20to%20news%20on%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20in%20response%20to%20a%20new%20law%20requiring%20digital%20giants%20to%20pay%20publishers%20for%20such%20content.%20Google%2C%20another%20critic%20of%20the%20Online%20News%20Act%2C%20has%20said%20it%20is%20considering%20a%20similar%20move%2C%20among%20an%20ongoing%20global%20debate%20as%20more%20governments%20try%20to%20make%20tech%20firms%20pay%20for%20news%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNews%20links%20and%20content%20posted%20by%20news%20publishers%20and%20broadcasters%20in%20Canada%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20viewable%20by%20people%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20Meta%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20posted%20on%20foreign%20sites%20will%20also%20not%20be%20viewable%20by%20Canadian%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20users%2C%20and%20they%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20share%20articles%20on%20the%20two%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20noted%20that%20the%20changes%20starting%20Tuesday%20would%20be%20implemented%20%26quot%3Bover%20the%20course%20of%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20reporter%20was%20still%20able%20to%20see%20news%20on%20Facebook%20Tuesday%2C%20but%20some%20users%20reported%20already%20getting%20messages%20saying%20such%20content%20was%20being%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Online%20News%20Act%20builds%20on%20similar%20legislation%20introduced%20in%20Australia%20and%20aims%20to%20support%20a%20struggling%20Canadian%20news%20sector%20that%20has%20seen%20a%20flight%20of%20advertising%20dollars%20and%20hundreds%20of%20publications%20closed%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20requires%20digital%20giants%20to%20make%20fair%20commercial%20deals%20with%20Canadian%20outlets%20for%20the%20news%20and%20information%20that%20is%20shared%20on%20their%20platforms%2C%20or%20face%20binding%20arbitration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20October%202022%20report%20by%20Canada's%20parliamentary%20budget%20watchdog%20estimated%20the%20legislation%20could%20see%20Canadian%20newspapers%20receive%20about%20Can%24330%20million%20(US%24250%20million)%20per%20year%20from%20digital%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20said%20the%20bill%20is%20flawed%20and%20based%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bincorrect%20premise%20that%20Meta%20benefits%20unfairly%20from%20news%20content%20shared%20on%20our%20platforms%2C%20when%20the%20reverse%20is%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20it%20said%2C%20news%20outlets%20share%20content%20on%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20to%20attract%20readers%2C%20which%20helps%20their%20own%20bottom%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20using%20our%20platforms%20don't%20come%20to%20us%20for%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Irresponsible'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeritage%20Minister%20Pascale%20St-Onge%20called%20the%20move%20to%20block%20news%20%26quot%3Birresponsible%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%2080%20percent%20of%20all%20online%20advertising%20revenues%20in%20Canada%20goes%20to%20Meta%20and%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20free%20and%20independent%20press%20is%20fundamental%20to%20our%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20other%20countries%20are%20considering%20introducing%20similar%20legislation%20%26quot%3Bto%20tackle%20the%20same%20challenges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada's%20public%20broadcaster%20slammed%20Meta's%20move%20as%20%26quot%3Birresponsible%20and%20an%20abuse%20of%20their%20market%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20Broadcasting%20Company%20(CBC)%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bcalling%20on%20Meta%20to%20act%20responsibly%20by%20restoring%20Canadians'%20access%20to%20news.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20Canadian%20media%20have%20taken%20a%20more%20complex%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20an%20editorial%20in%20the%20leading%20Globe%20and%20Mail%20newspaper%20suggested%20the%20bill%20%26quot%3Bdistorts%20the%20marketplace%20by%20protecting%20certain%20companies%20from%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20it%20called%20for%20tax%20credits%20for%20readers%20who%20subscribe%20to%20online%20news%20services%2C%20arguing%20that%20such%20a%20move%20would%20both%20%26quot%3Bpush%20newsrooms%20to%20innovate%26quot%3B%20and%20put%20the%20decision%20about%20who%20gets%20financial%20support%20into%20readers'%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20New%20Media%20Bargaining%20Code%20was%20a%20world%20first%20when%20it%20was%20rolled%20out%20in%202021%20to%20make%20Google%20and%20Meta%20pay%20for%20news%20content%20on%20their%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20saw%20significant%20pushback%20initially%20from%20both%20companies%20as%20they%20feared%20it%20would%20threaten%20their%20business%20models%2C%20but%20with%20amendments%20it%20was%20easily%20passed%20by%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690939620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fubcr6d58_meta_625x300_04_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmeta-is-blocking-news-on-facebook-instagram-in-canada-heres-why-4260945%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta%20on%20Wednesday%20started%20