here%20has%20been%20no%20success%20yet.%20There%20are%20over%206%2C000%20Zero%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20wanted%20his%20son%20becomes%20a%20scientist.%20The%20family%20was%20supposed%20to%20travel%20to%20Shillong%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20worked%20very%20hard%20and%20wanted%20me%20to%20join%20the%20ISRO's%20young%20scientist%20programme%20held%20in%20Shillong%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh's%20son%20Atom%20Thoihenba%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20our%20son%20to%20study%20in%20Delhi.%20How%20will%20I%20manage%20that%20now%20because%20he%20was%20the%20only%20earning%20member%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20mother%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20families%20should%20at%20least%20be%20given%20samples%20for%20DNA%20test%20so%20we%20can%20perform%20the%20last%20rites.%20But%20the%20Manipur%20government%20cannot%20do%20that%20and%20cannot%20find%20the%20missing%20persons%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Singh's%20uncle%20Atom%20Meghajit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExactly%20two%20months%20after%20the%20journalist%20and%20his%20friend%20went%20missing%2C%20another%20tragedy%20unfolded%20in%20Imphal%20on%20July%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHijam%20Luwangbi%20Linthoingambi%2C%2017%2C%20had%20left%20her%20home%20for%20her%20NEET%20coaching%20classes%20when%20the%20curfew%20was%20relaxed%20in%20the%20morning.%20She%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20her%20boyfriend%20%E2%80%93%2017-year-old%20Phijam%20Hemanjit%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20two%20went%20for%20a%20long%20ride%20on%20his%20bike%2C%20thinking%20the%20situation%20was%20improving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20been%20missing%20since.%20Their%20parents%20have%20filed%20complaints%20at%20two%20separate%20police%20stations.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20police%20say%20there%20is%20CCTV%20footage%20confirming%20they%20were%20spotted%20going%20towards%20Nambol%20area%20in%20Imphal%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCybercrime%20police%20reports%20that%20her%20phone%20was%20last%20switched%20off%20at%20Kwakta%20and%20the%20boy's%20phone%20got%20switched%20off%20at%20Lamdan%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hijam%20Kullajit%2C%20father%20of%20the%20girl.%20The%20two%20places%20are%20located%20in%20two%20different%20districts%20--%20Kwakta%20in%20Bishnpur%20district%2C%20Lamdan%20in%20Churachandpur%20%E2%80%93%20and%20are%2018%20km%20away%20from%20each%20other.%20The%20areas%20at%20the%20border%20of%20the%20valley%20and%20hills%20have%20seen%20major%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20she%20didn't%20return%2C%20I%20called%20her%20and%20she%20picked%20up.%20She%20seemed%20frightened%20and%20said%20she%20was%20in%20Nambol.%20I%20asked%20why%20she%20was%20at%20Nambol%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20reveal%20her%20location%2C%20so%20her%20father%20can%20come%20and%20pick%20her%20up.%20She%20murmured%20Khoupum%20(20%20km%20from%20Nambol)%20and%20her%20phone%20got%20switched%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20girl's%20mother%20Jayashree%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20are%20fearing%20that%20their%20loved%20ones%20are%20being%20tortured.%20Hemanjit's%20cellphone%20is%20now%20being%20used%20with%20a%20new%20number%2C%20the%20police%20have%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20area%20is%20just%2010%20km%20inside%20from%20the%20main%20road...%20the%20Tiddim%20road%2C%20but%20the%20police%20does%20not%20dare%20to%20go%20there%20to%20search%2C%26quot%3B%20Phijam%20Ibungobi%2C%20Hemanjit's%20father%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hills%2C%20the%20civil%20society%20has%20documented%20missing%20cases%20and%20also%20cases%20where%20the%20bodies%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20sent%20back.%20A%20mass%20burial%20has%20been%20planned%20on%20August%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20reports%20of%2044%20dead%20bodies%20of%20our%20people%20who%20went%20missing%20and%20are%20now%20in%20the%20morgues%20of%20Imphal%20hospitals.%20We%20have%20requested%20the%20authorities%20to%20send%20those%20bodies%20for%20burial%2C%26quot%3B%20said%