ifference%20towards%20Hindu%20beliefs%20and%20devotion%26quot%3B.%C2%A0The%20TTD%20issues%20a%20tender%20for%20ghee%20to%20make%20the%20world-famous%20Tirupati%20laddoos%2C%20which%20are%20given%20to%20devotees%20as%20%3Cem%3E'prasad'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(offering).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20leader%20C%20T%20Ravi%20has%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20state%20government%20increasing%20the%20price%20of%20Nandini%20milk%20made%20the%20Karnataka%20Milk%20Federation%20(KMF)%2C%20which%20owns%20the%20brand%2C%20uncompetitive%20in%20the%20bid%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20supply%20of%20Nandini%20ghee%20to%20the%20TTD%20has%20not%20happened%20for%20the%20past%20year-and-a-half%20and%20asked%20Mr%20Kateel%20whether%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20was%20in%20power%20at%20the%20time%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Banti-Hindu%20devotion%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister's%20claim%20was%20confirmed%20by%20KMF%20officials%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20last%20time%20Nandini%20ghee%20was%20supplied%20to%20the%20temple%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20in%202021.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20the%20last%20tender%20process%20was%20held%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tweet%20yesterday%2C%20Mr%20Kateel%20had%20quoted%20a%20media%20report%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20stopping%20supply%20of%20ghee%20from%20KMF%20for%20Tirupati%20laddoos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNandini%20ghee%20supply%20for%20Tirupati%20laddoos%20has%20been%20stopped%20due%20to%20%40INCKarnataka%20policy%20of%20indifference%20towards%20temple%2C%20and%20Hindu%20beliefs%20and%20devotion.%2050%20years%20of%20legacy%20with%20Tirupati%20is%20watered%20down%20and%20this%20proves%20%40siddaramaiah's%20policy%20of%20indifference%20towards%20Hindus%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tweet%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20cabinet%20had%20allowed%20KMF%20to%20increase%20the%20price%20of%20Nandini%20milk%20by%20Rs%203%20a%20litre%2C%20with%20effect%20from%20August%201.%20BJP%20leader%20CT%20Ravi%20said%20this%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20Nandini%20to%20supply%20milk%20to%20TTD%20at%20the%20earlier%20price.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20shamelessly%20politicised%20Nandini%20issue%20during%20the%20assembly%20elections%20and%20milked%20it%20to%20malign%20Amul...%20%C2%A0Thanks%20to%20the%20incompetent%20Congress%20government%2C%20Nandini%20will%20no%20longer%20supply%20ghee%20to%20prepare%20the%20famous%20Tirupati%20laddoos.%20It%20is%20very%20evident%20that%20Congress%20is%20bent%20on%20destroying%20Suvarna%20Karnataka%20to%20pursue%20its%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ravi%20tweeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20supply%20of%20Nandini%20ghee%20to%20Tirupati%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20has%20not%20been%20stopped%20today%20or%20yesterday.%20The%20supply%20of%20ghee%20to%20Tirupati%20was%20suspended%20one-and-a-half%20years%20ago%2C%20during%20the%20%40BJP4Karnataka%20government's%20tenure.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonorable%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20%40nalinkateel%2C%20tell%20me%20now%2C%20was%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20against%20Hindu%20religious%20beliefs%20and%20devotion%3F%20Or%20was%20only%20the%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20%40BSBommai%20(Basavaraj%20Bommai)%20anti-Hindu%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20life%20of%20the%20dairy%20farmers%20is%20important%20to%20us%20along%20with%20the%20religious%20faith%20of%20the%20people.%20Therefore%2C%20if%20the%20Tirupati%20temple%20agrees%20to%20give%20the%20price%20we%20ask%20for%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20state's%20farmers%2C%20we%20have%20no%20problem%20in%20supplying%20ghee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKMF%20chairperson%20Bheema%20Nayak%20has%20said%20the%20Nandini%20brand%20is%20known%20for%20its%20quality%20and%20cannot%20compromise%20on%20the%20price.%20He%20said%20the%20organisation%20had%2C%20thus%2C%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20tender%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20KMF%20officials%20said%20the%20tender%20process%20happens%20every%20six%20months%20and%20was%20last%20held%20in%20March%20this%20year.%20They%20added%20that%20a%20price%20increase%20in%20August%20would%20not%20affect%20the%20tendering%20process%20in%20March.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20KMF%20began%20supplying%20Nandini%20Ghee%20to%20the%20TTD%20in%202005%20and%20the%20last%20time%20its%20bid%20was%20partially%20successful%20was%20in%202021%2C%20when%20it%20got%2035%25%20of%20the%20supply%20contract%20after%20negotiations.%20%26quot%3BA%20bid%20was%20made%20in%202022%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20successful.%20We%20did%20not%20bid%20in%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20TTD%2C%20Dharma%20Reddy%2C%20said%20KMF%20had%20not%20participated%20in%20the%20last%20auction%20in%20March%202023.%20He%20also%20said%20all%20items%2C%20including%20ghee%20for%20laddoos%2C%20are%20bought%20through%20e-tenders%20and%20the%20lowest%20bidder%20is%20given%20the%20contract%2C%20provided%20the%20materials%20they%20supply%20conform%20to%20quality%20parameters%20set%20by%20the%20TTD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20a%20month%20before%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Congress%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20had%20said%20the%20Nandini%20brand%20would%20be%20threatened%20if%20Amul%20entered%20the%20state%20market.%20The%20parties%20had%20accused%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20of%20%26quot%3Blooting%26quot%3B%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20claimed%20the%20Congress%20was%20running%20a%20%26quot%3Bmisinformation%20campaign%26quot%3B%20and%20asserted%20that%20it%20has%20done%20far%20more%20than%20the%20opposition%20party%20to%20strengthen%20the%20KMF.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690910880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fue38ejp8_nandini-milk-outlet-pti_625x300_28_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnandini-milk-boils-up-karnataka-politics-again-now-with-a-religious-tinge-tirupati-laddoo-congress-bjp-4260406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%2C%20which%20was%20accused%20by%20the%20Congress%20of%20threatening%20the%20local%20Nandini%20dairy%20brand%20by%20allowing%20the%20entry%20of%20Amul%20in%20Karnataka%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20polls%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20is%20now%20attempting%20to%20turn%20the%20tables.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnandini-milk-boils-up-karnataka-politics-again-now-with-a-religious-tinge-tirupati-laddoo-congress-bjp-4260406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnandini-milk-boils-up-karnataka-politics-again-now-with-a-religious-tinge-tirupati-laddoo-congress-bjp-4260406%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnandini-milk-boils-up-karnataka-politics-again-now-with-a-religious-tinge-tirupati-laddoo-congress-bjp-4260406%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paris%20robbery%3A%20Smartly%20dressed%20gang%20stage%20%E2%82%AC10m%20jewellery%20raid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690910688000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0ECE%2Fproduction%2F_130609730_2e3dff22d8b12ff7d01117f993f42ad2d056ea400_32_5313_29881000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66372354%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20men%20in%20suits%20and%20a%20woman%20wearing%20a%20dress%20target%20a%20store%20in%20a%20street%20full%20of%20luxury%20jewellery%20shops.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A86%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66372354%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66372354.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66372354.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nuh%20Clashes%20Well-Coordinated%2C%20More%20Such%20Violence%20Likely%20Ahead%20of%202024%20Polls%3A%20Satyapal%20Malik%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F16125509%2FScreenshot-2023-04-16-at-12.55.00-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFormer%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20governor%20Satyapal%20Malik%20said%20the%20violence%20that%20began%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Nuh%20and%20spread%20to%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20was%20not%20spontaneous.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20attacks%20in%20seven%20to%20eight%20different%20places%20were%20well-coordinated%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20creating%20a%20communal%20divide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20country%20will%20burn%20like%20Manipur%20if%20these%20people%20are%20not%20contained%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CJats%20by%20culture%20or%20tradition%20believe%20in%20the%20Arya%20Samaj%20way%20of%20life%20and%20are%20not%20very%20religious%20in%20the%20traditional%20sense%20of%20the%20term.%20Neither%20are%20the%20Muslims%20of%20this%20area%20very%20traditional%20in%20their%20outlook.%20Therefore%20one%20has%20never%20heard%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20clashing%20in%20this%20manner%20ever%20since%20Independence.%20And%20these%20attacks%20will%20only%20increase%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%202024%20as%20is%20evident%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20addressing%20a%20packed%20hall%20at%20the%20Constitution%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convention%20on%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%20affairs%E2%80%9D%2C%20organised%20by%20six%20groups%20of%20social%20activists%2C%20also%20passed%20two%20resolutions%20on%20the%20Pulwama%20and%20the%20Balakot%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20demanded%20the%20government%20to%20make%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20report%20public%20along%20with%20an%20action-taken%20report%2C%20including%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20lapses%20and%20action%20taken%20against%20those%20involved.%20They%20also%20said%20a%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20committee%20should%20probe%20the%20Pulwama%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20assembled%20also%20demanded%20an%20increase%20in%20security%20at%20various%20pilgrim%20sites.%20They%20feared%20that%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20an%20attack%20could%20be%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20under-construction%20Ram%20Mandir%20at%20Ayodhya%20or%20any%20of%20the%20other%20prominent%20temples%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20be%20done%20by%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20to%20polarise%20the%20public%20and%20win%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20said.%20An%20alleged%20threat%20by%20Al-Qaeda%20that%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20would%20be%20blown%20up%20should%20be%20taken%20seriously%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gathering%20was%20addressed%20by%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20Digvijay%20Singh%2C%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20Kumar%20Ketkar%2C%20John%20Brittas%2C%20and%20lawyer%20Prashant%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20going%20by%20the%20audience%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20Satyapal%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20interest%20in%20what%20happened%20at%20Pulwama%20or%20Balakot%20has%20not%20waned.%20While%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20allegations%20that%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20was%20done%20by%20the%20Indian%20establishment%20were%20discussed%20in%20whispers%2C%20now%20all%20prominent%20speakers%20openly%20voiced%20their%20apprehension%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20not%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20Pulwama%2C%20Modi%20milked%20the%20tragedy%20and%20told%20crowds%20to%20remember%20Pulwama%20when%20they%20vote.%20I%20tell%20the%20crowds%20once%20again%2C%20remember%20Pulwama%20when%20you%20vote%20this%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Malik.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20several%20unanswered%20questions.%20Where%20did%20the%20RDX%20come%20from%3F%20Why%20was%20the%20route%20not%20sanitised%20or%20manned%20by%20anyone%20for%2010%20kilometres%20either%20side%3F%20Why%20was%20the%20aircraft%20refused%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContradicting%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20who%20said%20there%20were%2011%20intelligence%20reports%20ahead%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20Malik%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20governor%2C%20I%20used%20to%20get%20three%20intelligence%20reports%20a%20day%2C%20each%20detailing%20a%20terror%20attack%20that%20could%20happen%20to%20me%20or%20to%20the%20establishment.%20I%20was%20warned%20by%20the%20Army%20not%20to%20travel%20by%20road%20but%20take%20a%20chopper%20and%20so%20on.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20single%20intelligence%20report%20that%20an%20Army%20convoy%20could%20be%20attacked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalik%20said%20something%20similar%20could%20be%20planned%20in%202024.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20could%20kill%20a%20prominent%20BJP%20leader%20or%20throw%20a%20bomb%20at%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20Why%20is%20Ajit%20Doval%20(National%20Security%20Advisor)%20frequenting%20the%20UAE%20now%20a%20days%3F%20He%20is%20drumming%20up%20support%20from%20the%20rulers%20there%20that%20they%20should%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20Pakistanis%20not%20to%20retaliate%20when%20our%20troops%20enter%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir.%20They%20will%20stay%20there%20for%20a%20few%20days%20and%20come%20back%20and%20hope%20to%20win%20the%20election.%20People%20should%20know%20what%20they%20are%20up%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690910397000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20