t%20propelled%20Angus%20Cloud%20to%20fame.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A87%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66374070%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66374070.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-66374070.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22It's%20Our%20Right%20To%20Oppose%5C%22%3A%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20On%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20on%20Tuesday%20opposed%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20our%20right%20to%20oppose%20the%20bill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20brief%20introduction%20on%20the%20Delhi%20(NCT)%20Ordinance%20Bill%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Parliament%20today.%20However%2C%20only%20an%20introduction%20was%20held%20and%20not%20a%20debate%20on%20it.%20It%20is%20our%20right%20to%20oppose%20the%20introduction%20and%20five%20to%20six%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20tried%20to%20oppose%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%2C%20one%20of%20the%20parties%20from%20the%20opposition%20supported%20the%20government.%20Others%20said%20that%20it%20is%20illegal%20and%20that%20the%20government%20is%20taking%20unconstitutional%20actions%26quot%3B%2C%20added%20Shashi%20Tharoor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20bill%20to%20replace%20the%20ordinance%20for%20control%20of%20services%20in%20Delhi%20was%20introduced%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%20The%20controversial%20bill%20aims%20to%20replace%20an%20ordinance%20that%20granted%20the%20Centre%20control%20over%20Delhi's%20bureaucrats%2C%20thereby%20overriding%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20favouring%20the%20elected%20government's%20authority%20in%20transfers%20and%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Nityanand%20Rai%20introduced%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20members%20including%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20NK%20Premachandran%20and%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20opposed%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20rise%20to%20oppose%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20bill%20as%20the%20bill%20vindicates%20the%20outrageous%20infringement%20of%20this%20govt%20upon%20the%20territory%20of%20the%20state.%20It%20is%20designed%20of%20digging%20up%20a%20graveyard%20for%20cooperative%20federalism.%20The%20state%20has%20rights%20over%20the%20subject%20centre%20is%20overriding%20powers%2C%26quot%3B%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevolutionist%20Socialist%20Party%20MP%20NK%20Premachandran%20questioned%20the%20legislative%20competence%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20over%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20meaning%20of%20government%20in%20delhi%20if%20this%20bill%20gets%20passed.%20It%20is%20taking%20away%20legislative%20powers%20from%20the%20elected%20government%20through%20bureaucrats.%20It%20is%20overriding%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20said%20that%20this%20bill%20is%20violating%20multiple%20provisions%20of%20the%20constitution.%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20Article%20123.%20It%20is%20violating%20the%20separation%20of%20powers%20theory.%20There%20is%20no%20legislative%20competence.%20I%20demand%20a%20division%20of%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERejecting%20the%20contentions%20of%20opposition%20members%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20Constitution%20has%20given%20the%20House%20power%20to%20pass%20any%20law%20regarding%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20has%20clarified%20that%20parliament%20can%20bring%20any%20law%20regarding%20Delhi%20and%20the%20opposition%20parties%20were%20opposing%20its%20introduction%20for%20political%20considerations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20empowers%20the%20Central%20Government%20to%20make%20rules%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20including%20the%20functions%2C%20terms%20and%20other%20conditions%20of%20service%20of%20officers%20and%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20on%20May%2019%20introduced%20the%20Ordinance%20for%20control%20of%20services%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20ordinance%20was%20introduced%20days%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690909500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fcpr73q6o_shashi-tharoor_625x300_01_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fits-our-right-to-oppose-shashi-tharoor-on-delhi-services-bill-4260104%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20on%20Tuesday%20opposed%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20our%20right%20to%20oppose%20the%20bill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fits-our-right-to-oppose-shashi-tharoor-on-delhi-services-bill-4260104%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fits-our-right-to-oppose-shashi-tharoor-on-delhi-services-bill-4260104%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fits-our-right-to-oppose-shashi-tharoor-on-delhi-services-bill-4260104%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Troubling%20But%20Not%20Unduly%20Alarming'%3A%20Centre%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Cheetah%20Deaths%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01124706%2FFr_KjcBXoAEm2rW.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20and%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20(NTCA)%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2031%2C%20that%20a%20provisional%20diagnosis%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20that%20have%20occurred%20at%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20%E2%80%9Cpoints%20towards%20natural%20causes%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fcheetah-deaths-at-kuno-national-park-troubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-ntca-to-sc%2F621263.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deaths%20are%20%E2%80%9Ctroubling%E2%80%9D%20but%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20unduly%20alarming%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20government%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20the%20court%20had%20asked%20that%20a%20detailed%20affidavit%20explaining%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%2C%20and%20the%20remedial%20measures%20being%20taken%2C%20be%20submitted.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%20five%20adult%20cheetahs%20and%20three%20cubs%20have%20died%20in%20Kuno%20%E2%80%93%20where%2020%20cheetahs%20were%20brought%20from%20South%20Africa%20and%20Namibia%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20African%20cheetah%20transcontinental%20relocation%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Not%20unduly%20alarming%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20%E2%80%93%20while%20hearing%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20that%20the%20NTCA%20no%20longer%20needs%20to%20take%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20expert%20committee%20appointed%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20through%20an%20order%20dated%20January%2028%2C%202020%2C%20for%20cheetah%20introduction%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20had%20raised%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeaths%20of%20the%20African%20cheetahs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20Kuno.%20It%20had%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20file%20a%20detailed%20affidavit%20explaining%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%2C%20and%20the%20remedial%20measures%20being%20taken.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20and%20NTCA%2C%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Finquiry-into-cheetahs-deaths-points-to-natural-causes-centre-informs-sc%2Farticle67143291.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edetailed%20affidavit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20said%20that%20the%20provisional%20diagnosis%20of%20deaths%20points%20towards%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20none%20of%20the%20cheetahs%20have%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cunnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%20such%20as%20poaching%2C%20snaring%2C%20poisoning%2C%20road%20hits%2C%20electrocution%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20respectfully%20submitted%20that%20the%20NTCA%20today%20has%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20mortalities%20were%20caused%20on%20account%20of%20any%20inherent%20unsuitability%20at%20the%20Kuno%20site%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20affidavit%20said%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fcheetah-deaths-at-kuno-national-park-troubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-ntca-to-sc%2F621263.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%20report%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20affidavit%20also%20claimed%20that%20cheetahs%20have%20a%20very%20low%20survival%20rate%20even%20in%20non-introduced%20or%20native%20populations.%20In%20introduced%20populations%2C%20the%20survival%20rates%20are%20even%20lower%2C%20it%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20case%20of%20introduced%20population%2C%20the%20survival%20rates%20are%20even%20much%20lower%20taking%20other%20variables%20into%20account%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20about%2010%25%20survival%20in%20cubs%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20mortalities%20(at%20KNP)%20though%20troubling%20and%20in%20need%20of%20redressal%20and%20curtailment%20are%20not%20unduly%20alarming%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fcheetah-deaths-at-kuno-national-park-troubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-ntca-to-sc%2F621263.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaffidavit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFurther%2C%20for%20veterinary%20care%2C%20day-to-day%20management%20and%20monitoring%20and%20other%20specific%20aspects%20related%20to%20ecology%20and%20behaviour%20of%20cheetahs%20is%20being%20done%20in%20consultation%20with%20internationally%20experienced%20cheetah%20experts%2C%20when%20and%20where%20required%2C%20and%20in%20conformity%20with%20the%20scientific%20Action%20Plan.%20The%20best%20possible%20veterinary%20support%20and%20health%20care%20is%20provided%20to%20the%20cheetahs%20to%20ensure%20their%20survival%20in%20the%20natural%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20affidavit%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fcheetah-deaths-at-kuno-national-park-troubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-ntca-to-sc%2F621263.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20have%20said.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20prophylactic%20treatment%20is%20being%20administered%20to%20all%20surviving%20cheetahs%20and%20that%20a%20review%20of%20project%20implementation%20is%20being%20undertaken.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdrian%20Tordiffe%2C%20South%20African%20wildlife%20veterinarian%20who%20is%20also%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20had%20first%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20level%20of%20veterinary%20care%20available%20at%20Kuno%20while%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espeaking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20July%2015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETordiffe%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Rajesh%20Gopal%2C%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Steering%20Committee%2C%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20deaths%20of%20two%20adult%20cheetahs%2C%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%2C%20were%20caused%20by%20radio%20collar-caused%20infections.%20The%20NTCA%20on%20July%2016%20had%20denied%20this%20claim%20and%20insisted%20that%20all%20animals%20died%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIdentified%20other%20sites%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20joint%20affidavit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Flegal%2Fkuno-deaths-govt-identifies-potential-sites-in-mp-rajasthan-for-cheetah-introduction%2F621328.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20apart%20from%20Kuno%20National%20Park%2C%20authorities%20have%20identified%20potential%20sites%20for%20cheetah%20introduction%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20These%20include%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20and%20Nauradehi%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Shahgarh%20Bulge%2C%20Bhainsrorgarh%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20and%20enclosure%20of%20Mukundra%20Hills%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20Rajasthan.%20However%2C%20Mukundra%20Hills%20is%20at%20present%20not%20fit%20for%20accommodating%20cheetahs%2C%20per%20the%20affidavit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20and%20its%20extended%20landscape%20of%206800%20per%20sq.km%2C%20the%20NTCA%20has%20requested%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20June%2028%20to%20add%20areas%20in%20Shivpuri%2C%20Sheopur%20divisions%20and%20Heerupur%20wildlife%20sanctuary%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Finquiry-into-cheetahs-deaths-points-to-natural-causes-centre-informs-sc%2Farticle67143291.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Currently%2C%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20and%20Nauradehi%20are%20being%20prepared%20for%20the%20cheetah%20population%2C%20the%20affidavit%20also%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690909232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01124706%2FFr_KjcBXoAEm2rW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftroubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-centre-to-supreme-court-on-cheetah-deaths%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20joint%20affidavit%20by%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20and%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20stated%20that%20a%20provisional%20diagnosis%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20'points%20towards%20natural%20causes'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftroubling-but-not-unduly-alarming-centre-to-supreme-court-on-cheetah-deaths%22%2C%22