31%20July%2C%20the%20final%20day%20for%20filing%2C%20the%20number%20of%20ITRs%20peaked%20with%20over%206.433%20million%20ITRs%20submitted%20in%20a%20single%20day%2C%20the%20I-T%20department%20reported%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ftax-filing-for-ay24-touches-all-time-high-surpasses-67-7-million-123080100964_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ftax-filing-for-ay24-touches-all-time-high-surpasses-67-7-million-123080100964_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ftax-filing-for-ay24-touches-all-time-high-surpasses-67-7-million-123080100964_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Reducing%20Footprints%5C%22%3A%20Centre%20On%20Pak's%20Drone%20Strategy%20To%20Ferry%20Weapons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20infiltration%20levels%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20declined%2C%20but%20Pakistan%20is%20keeping%20terrorism%20alive%20and%20using%20technology%20to%20send%20weapons%20and%20drugs%20into%20India%20through%20drones%2C%20the%20centre%20told%20parliament%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20said%20anti-national%20elements%20and%20smugglers%20are%20using%20drones%20for%20smuggling%20of%20arms%20and%20narcotics%20across%20the%20India-Pakistan%20border%20in%20Punjab%20and%2053%20such%20incidents%20were%20detected%20in%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20reply%2C%20the%20ministry%20also%20stated%20that%20no%20infiltration%20has%20been%20reported%20till%20June-end%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20is%20reducing%20its%20footprints%20so%20that%20nothing%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20them%20that's%20why%20they%20have%20been%20using%20drones%20to%20ferry%20weapons%20from%20across%20border.%20Many%20consignments%20have%20been%20traced%20some%20also%20go%20untraced%20and%20they%20reach%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20charge%20of%20operations%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20weapons%20and%20narcotics%20used%20to%20reach%20J%26amp%3BK%20via%20trade%20routes%2C%20according%20to%20him%2C%20but%20now%20they%20have%20adopted%20new%20ways.%20%26quot%3BPakistan%20does%20not%20want%20to%20get%20on%20wrong%20foot%20but%20is%20using%20narcotics%20to%20feed%20youngsters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20modus%20operandi%20of%20Pakistan%20was%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20ministry%20reply%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday.%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Nisith%20Pramanik%20said%20anti-national%20elements%20and%20smugglers%20are%20using%20drones%20for%20smuggling%20of%20arms%20and%20narcotics%20across%20India-Pakistan%20border%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20three%20years%20and%20till%20June%2030%20this%20year%2C%20a%20total%20of%2053%20incidents%20of%20use%20of%20drones%20in%20smuggling%20of%20arms%20and%20narcotics%20have%20been%20detected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNumber%20of%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20that%20include%20effective%20round%20the%20clock%20domination%20of%20the%20borders%20by%20the%20BSF%2C%20surveillance%2C%20patrolling%2C%20laying%20of%20nakas%2C%20manning%20of%20observation%20posts%20all%20along%20the%20International%20Border%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pramanik%20stated%20in%20his%20written%20reply%20adding%20that%20local%20police%20is%20immediately%20informed%20as%20soon%20any%20drone%20movement%20is%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20general%20public%20in%20border%20areas%20have%20been%20sensitised%20and%20made%20aware%20of%20such%20UAV%20and%20drone%20activities%20and%20their%20likely%20security%20implications.%20They%20are%20encouraged%20to%20inform%20about%20any%20such%20activities%20in%20the%20rear%20areas%20to%20the%20BSF%20as%20well%20as%20the%20local%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20MHA%20has%20established%20Anti%20Rogue%20Drone%20Technology%20Committee%20(ARDTC)%20under%20supervision%20of%20the%20DG%20BSF%20with%20mandate%20to%20evaluate%20the%20technology%20available%20to%20counter%20rogue%20drones%20and%20certify%20its%20effectiveness%20in%20dealing%20with%20rouge%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20in%20another%20reply%20the%20MHA%20stated%20that%20only%2026%20terror%20related%20incidents%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20first%20six%20months%20this%20year.%20But%20last%20year%20as%20many%20as%20125%20terror%20related%20incidents%20and%2014%20successful%20infiltration%20were%20reported.%20While%20in%202021%2C%20134%20terror%20incidents%20and%2034%20successful%20infiltration%20attempts%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeasures%20being%20taken%20by%20the%20government%20to%20curb%20terrorist%20violence%20include%20proactive%20counter%20insurgency%20operations%20against%20terrorists%2C%20identification%20and%20arrest%20of%20over%20ground%20supporters%20of%20terrorists%2C%20deployment%20of%20police%2C%20Army%2C%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPFs)%20and%20night%20patrolling%20and%20area%20domination%2C%26quot%3B%20Minister%20for%20State%20(Home%20Affairs%20Nityanand%20Rai%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20attachment%20of%20properties%20belonging%20to%20terrorists%20and%20their%20associates%20under%20relevant%20sections%20of%20law%2C%20sharing%20of%20intelligence%20inputs%20amongst%20all%20security%20forces%20on%20a%20real-time%20basis%20and%20intensified%20Cordon%20and%20Search%20Operations%20(CASO)%20are%20also%20undertaken%20to%20thwart%20any%20terrorist%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMulti-tiered%20deployment%20along%20IB%2FLoC%2C%20border%20fencing%2C%20deployment%20of%20intelligence%20personnel%20to%20collect%20advance%20and%20target-oriented%20inputs%20on%20infiltration%2C%20ambushes%20and%20footpatrolling%20by%20Army%20and%20Border%20Security%20Force%2C%20establishment%20of%20border%20police%20posts%20for%20generating%20local%20intelligence%20and%20taking%20pro-active%20action%20against%20infiltrators%20are%20other%20action%20taken%20by%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690903980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fvpa31mb_jammu-and-kashmir-security-generic-ndtv_625x300_07_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-using-technology-to-send-weapons-drones-into-india-centre-4260052%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20infiltration%20levels%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20declined%2C%20but%20Pakistan%20is%20keeping%20terrorism%20alive%20and%20using%20technology%20to%20send%20weapons%20and%20drugs%20into%20India%20through%20drones%2C%20the%20centre%20told%20parliament%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-using-technology-to-send-weapons-drones-into-india-centre-4260052%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-using-technology-to-send-weapons-drones-into-india-centre-4260052%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpak-using-technology-to-send-weapons-drones-into-india-centre-4260052%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Okay%20To%20Be..%5C%22%3A%20Straight-faced%20Pandya%20Shuts%20Down%20WI%20Star's%20Tricky%20Query%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20second%20match%20running%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20the%20O