90901633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10CA2%2Fproduction%2F_130607786_2f1b41e08e8d17e4a04cb837ef1f9bbe15cb6dc2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66374032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20I%20think%20this%20is%20our%20new%20reality%26quot%3B%20one%20resident%20of%20the%20Russian%20capital%20told%20the%20BBC.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A64%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66374032%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66374032.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66374032.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indira%20Gandhi%20Had%20Good%20Relations%20With%20Many%20RSS%20Leaders%2C%20But...%3A%20Book%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20had%20good%20relations%20with%20several%20RSS%20leaders%2C%20and%20just%20as%20the%20Sangh%20brass%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20for%20help%2C%20she%20too%20used%20it%20for%20her%20purposes%20but%20carefully%20kept%20a%20distance%20between%20the%20organisation%20and%20herself%2C%20claims%20a%20new%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BHow%20Prime%20Ministers%20Decide%26quot%3B%2C%20journalist%20Neerja%20Chowdhury%20analyses%20the%20operating%20styles%20of%20the%20country's%20Prime%20Ministers%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20six%20decisions%20of%20historic%20significance%20-%20the%20strategy%20that%20(Indira)%20Gandhi%20devised%20to%20return%20to%20power%20in%201980%20post-Emergency%2C%20the%20Shah%20Bano%20case%2C%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%2C%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20incident%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20nod%20to%20nuclear%20tests%2C%20and%20the%20Indo-US%20nuclear%20deal%20under%20Manmohan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20claims%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20had%20made%20overtures%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%20all%20through%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRSS%20chief%20Balasaheb%20Deoras%20had%20written%20to%20her%20several%20times.%20Some%20RSS%20leaders%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20through%20Kapil%20Mohan.%20Now%2C%20in%201977%2C%20she%20would%20have%20to%20see%20how%20to%20respond.%20But%20she%20would%20have%20to%20play%20this%20one%20very%20carefully%2C%26quot%3B%20Neerja%20Chowdhury%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20the%20RSS%20brass%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20for%20help%2C%20she%20too%20used%20the%20RSS%20for%20her%20purposes%20-%20but%20carefully%20kept%20a%20distance%20between%20the%20organisation%20and%20herself.%20For%20all%20her%20opposition%20to%20the%20RSS%2C%20she%20had%20managed%20to%20get%20it%20to%20support%20the%20Emergency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20the%20unhappiness%20amongst%20Muslims%20about%20the%20Congress%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3BHinduize%20her%20politics%26quot%3B%2C%20aware%20that%20a%20silent%20nudge%20from%20the%20RSS%20or%20even%20a%20neutral%20stand%20by%20them%20towards%20her%20might%20help%2C%20Neerja%20Chowdhury%20says%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20author%2C%20her%20book%20is%20about%20power%20and%20its%20exercise%20by%20those%20who%20held%20the%20highest%20public%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chapters%20illustrate%20how%20the%20power%20of%20the%20prime%20ministers%20played%20out%20under%20majority%20rule%20as%20well%20as%20in%20a%20coalition%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20also%20claims%20that%20in%201980%2C%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20was%20trying%20to%20secularize%20his%20image%20while%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20trying%20to%20Hinduize%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RSS%20helped%20Indira%20Gandhi%20come%20to%20power%20in%201980%2C%26quot%3B%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20close%20aide%20Anil%20Bali%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20knew%20the%20RSS%20had%20supported%20her%20but%20she%20never%20acknowledged%20it%20publicly.%20She%20used%20to%20admit%20privately%20that%20had%20it%20not%20been%20for%20the%20support%20by%20the%20RSS%2C%20she%20could%20not%20have%20won%20353%20seats%2C%20one%20more%20than%20she%20had%20won%20in%20her%20heyday%20in%201971%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bali%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20%26quot%3Bincreased%20temple%20going%20was%20not%20lost%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20RSS%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRSS%20chief%20Balasaheb%20Deoras%20had%20once%20remarked%20during%20the%20course%20of%20a%20conversation%2C%20'Indira%20Gandhi%20bahut%20badi%20Hindu%20hai%20(Indira%20Gandhi%20is%20a%20staunch%20Hindu).'%20%26quot%3BBalasaheb%20Deoras%20and%20his%20brother%20saw%20in%20Indira%20Gandhi%20a%20potential%20leader%20of%20the%20Hindus%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bali%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soon%20to%20be%20launched%20book%2C%20published%20by%20Aleph%20Book%20Company%2C%20also%20says%20the%20RSS%20in%201971%20praised%20Indira%20Gandhi%20for%20hiving%20off%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20weakening%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20then%20RSS%20chief%20Madhav%20Sadashiv%20Golwalkar%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Guruji%2C%20wrote%20to%20her%2C%20'The%20biggest%20measure%20of%20credit%20for%20this%20achievement%20goes%20to%20you.'%20In%201974%2C%20she%20won%20the%20RSS's%20admiration%20again%20for%20exploding%20the%20nuclear%20device%20-%20the%20RSS%20had%20always%20advocated%20a%20militarily%20strong%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeerja%20Chowdhury%20also%20writes%20that%20what%20V%20P%20Singh%20did%2C%20no%20one%20else%20who%20had%20left%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20years%20had%20managed%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20Chandra%20Shekhar%2C%20nor%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20nor%20Ramkrishna%20Hegde%2C%20nor%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20nor%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy.%20They%20too%20had%2C%20like%20VP%2C%20severed%20relations%20with%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20in%20the%201970s%2C%201980s%2C%20and%201990s%20in%20the%20last%20century%2C%20and%20also%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHegde%2C%20Pawar%2C%20Banerjee%2C%20Reddy%20went%20on%20to%20replace%20the%20Congress%20in%20their%20states%20and%20became%20chief%20ministers%2C%20ironically%20sometimes%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20they%20had%20quit.%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20had%20become%20prime%20minister%20at%20the%20head%20of%20a%20rump%20supported%20by%20the%20larger%2C%20domineering%20Congress.%26quot%3B%20But%20none%20had%20managed%20to%20create%20a%20national%20alternative%20to%20the%20Congress%20like%20Singh%20did%2C%20though%20it%20lasted%20just%20under%20a%20year%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20brought%20together%20almost%20all%20the%20anti-Congress%20forces%2C%20of%20the%20Right%2C%20Left%2C%20Centre%2C%20and%20the%20regional%20parties%20on%20one%20platform%20in%20the%20first%20truly%20national%20coalition.%20It%20was%20a%20three-tiered%20arrangement%2C%20in%20what%20was%20a%20rare%20show%20of%20Opposition%20unity.%20He%20gave%20the%20regional%20parties%20a%20stake%20in%20national%20governance%20at%20the%20centre%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20book%20says.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690901400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-01%2Findira-gandhi_650x400_61485498390.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-had-good-relations-with-many-rss-leaders-but-book-4258942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indira%20Gandhi%20had%20good%20relations%20with%20several%20RSS%20leaders%2C%20and%20just%20as%20the%20Sangh%20brass%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20for%20help%2C%20she%20too%20used%20it%20for%20her%20purposes%20but%20carefully%20kept%20a%20distance%20between%20the%20organisation%20and%20herself%2C%20claims%20a%20new%20book.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-had-good-relations-with-many-rss-leaders-but-book-4258942%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-had-good-relations-with-many-rss-leaders-but-book-4258942%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-had-good-relations-with-many-rss-leaders-but-book-4258942%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dead%20For%2010%20Years%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Teacher%20Gets%20Rs%207-Crore%20Tax%20Notice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20government-school%20teacher%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20received%20a%20tax%20notice%20of%20a%20staggering%20Rs%207%20crore.%20What%20has%20stunned%20her%20family%20even%20more%20than%20the%20amount%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20the%20teacher%20had%20died%20in%202013%20and%20the%20notice%20pertains%20to%20the%20assessment%20year%202017-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20is%20not%20alone.%20Sources%20in%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20said%20as%20many%20as%2044%20people%20in%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Betul%20district%20have%20received%20tax%20demand%20notices%20of%20amounts%20ranging%20from%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20Rs%2010%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20Soni%20was%20a%20teacher%20in%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Patkheda%20village.%20On%20July%2026%2C%20her%20family%20received%20a%20notice%20from%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%2C%20ordering%20the%20payment%20of%20Rs%207.55%20crore%20in%20tax%20dues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20son%2C%20Pawan%20Soni%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20mother%20died%20on%2016%20November%2C%202013%2C%20after%20a%20long%20illness.%20The%20notice%20is%20for%20the%202017-18%20assessment%20year.%20The%20document%20mentions%20a%20company%20called%20'Natural%20Costing'%2C%20which%20was%20engaged%20in%20buying%20and%20selling%20scrap%20materials.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint.%20My%20mother's%20PAN%20(Permanent%20Account%20Number)%20has%20been%20misused%20and%20we%20did%20not%20even%20know%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Soni%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20Jain%20who%20earns%20between%20Rs%205%2C000%20and%20Rs%207%2C000%20a%20month%20by%20working%20at%20a%20shop%20selling%20iron%20rods%2C%20was%20shocked%20after%20receiving%20a%20demand%20notice%20of%20Rs%201.26%20crore.%20When%20he%20went%20to%20the%20income%20tax%20office%2C%20he%20found%20that%20there%20is%20an%20account%20in%20his%20name%20in%20Courtallam%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20town%20he%20has%20never%20even%20heard%20the%20name%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22kqocped8%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fkqocped8_nitin-jain-tax-notice_625x300_01_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20Jain%2C%20who%20works%20at%20a%20shop%20selling%20iron%20rods%2C%20has%20received%20a%20tax%20demand%20notice%20of%20Rs%201.26%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20told%20me%20the%20account%20was%20opened%20in%20my%20name%20in%202014-15%20and%20several%20huge%20transactions%20have%20taken%20place%20since%2C%20because%20of%20which%20I%20was%20sent%20a%20notice%20of%20Rs%201.26%20crore.%20I%20have%20lodged%20an%20FIR%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetul%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Siddharth%20Choudhary%20said%20they%20have%20received%20two%20complaints%20of%20PAN%20misuse%20so%20far.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20people%20have%20complained%20that%20they%20did%20not%20own%20the%20business%20or%20account%20mentioned%20in%20the%20income%20tax%20notice%20and%20that%20their%20PAN%20cards%20have%20been%20misused.%20A%20detailed%20inquiry%20has%20been%2