0stories%20are%20still%20swollen%20with%20the%20exaggerations%20that%20make%20some%20men%20impossibly%20broad-chested%20and%20lion-hearted%20and%20the%20rest%20just%20men%E2%80%9D.%20During%20a%20school%20trip%20to%20Humayun%E2%80%99s%20Tomb%2C%20one%20of%20his%20pupils%20addresses%20him%20with%20a%20religious%20slur%20and%2C%20instinctively%20and%20uncharacteristically%2C%20Alif%20responds%20by%20reaching%20out%20and%20twisting%20his%20ear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reverberations%20of%20this%20act%20are%20the%20framework%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20novel.%20However%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%E2%80%99s%20Angel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20not%20simply%20a%20linear%20progression%20of%20events%3A%20it%20is%20an%20informed%20exploration%20of%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20milieu%2C%20with%20his%20family%20and%20friends%20providing%20the%20necessary%20shades%20and%20contrasts%20for%20a%20portrayal%20of%20a%20cross-section%20of%20Muslims%20in%20north%20India%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOthers%20on%20this%20spectrum%20of%20faith%20and%20hope%20include%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Tahira%2C%20a%20store%20manager%20at%20a%20Karol%20Bagh%20supermarket%20who%20is%20studying%20for%20an%20MBA%20and%20whose%20weekends%20are%20given%20over%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20which%20makes%20the%20world%20go%20round%2C%20or%20so%20say%20Dale%20Carnegie%20and%20Steven%20Covey%E2%80%9D.%20Their%20teenage%20son%20often%20puzzles%20Alif%20by%20his%20fascination%20with%20technology%20and%20the%20digital%20world%2C%20as%20does%20the%20attitude%20of%20his%20practical%20cousin%2C%20owner%20of%20a%20shoe%20store%2C%20who%20dreams%20of%20moving%20to%20the%20Emirates%20and%20urges%20Alif%20to%20manage%20the%20shop%20in%20his%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%20ripples%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20existence%20arrive%20in%20the%20form%20of%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20the%20tempestuous%20life%20of%20his%20close%20friend%20Ganesh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20bit%20too%20fond%20of%20the%20bottle.%20Ganesh%20nurtures%20feelings%20for%20an%20old%20school%20crush%20and%2C%20to%20his%20surprise%2C%20Alif%20finds%20himself%20feeling%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20ageing%20parents%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20do%20the%20best%20they%20can%20to%20survive%20in%20changing%20circumstances.%20Much%20of%20their%20time%20is%20spent%20in%20keeping%20tabs%20on%20relatives%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20their%20increasingly%20radicalised%20domestic%20help.%20The%20rest%20is%20spent%20in%20watching%20cooking%20shows%20and%20news%20on%20TV%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20inevitably%20posing%20the%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20does%20it%20mean%2C%20sir%2C%20to%20be%20a%20Muslim%20in%20contemporary%20India%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislam-christianity-conversion-hindutva-violence%5C%22%3ENo%20Country%20for%20Religious%20Converts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20lives%20are%20suffused%20by%20a%20feeling%20that%20Orhan%20Pamuk%20once%20described%20as%20%3Cem%3Eh%C3%BCz%C3%BCn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20melancholy.%20This%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20softens%20the%20view%20%E2%80%9Clike%20the%20condensation%20on%20a%20window%20when%20a%20teakettle%20has%20been%20spouting%20steam%20on%20a%20winter%E2%80%99s%20day%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbove%20and%20beyond%20these%20characters%20is%20the%20city%20of%20Delhi%20itself%2C%20which%20Hasan%20portrays%20in%20hues%20that%20alternate%20between%20the%20gaudy%2C%20the%20shop-worn%20and%20the%20materialistic.%20Her%20characters%20move%20through%20the%20teeming%20streets%20and%20residences%20of%20the%20old%20city%2C%20survey%20the%20grandeur%20of%20its%20monuments%2C%20and%20test%20themselves%20against%20the%20brashness%20of%20its%20ritzy%20malls%20and%20new%20habitations.%20Delhi%2C%20thinks%20Alif%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20city%20on%20which%20the%20apocalypse%20descends%20every%20day%20and%20the%20city%20where%20the%20apocalypse%20is%20always%20awaited%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160421%2F0ABAF2E0-4BC7-493A-A8BA-880B8A8704AB_1_105_c.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160421%2F0ABAF2E0-4BC7-493A-A8BA-880B8A8704AB_1_105_c.jpeg%20886w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160421%2F0ABAF2E0-4BC7-493A-A8BA-880B8A8704AB_1_105_c-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01160421%2F0ABAF2E0-4BC7-493A-A8BA-880B8A8704AB_1_105_c-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666112%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20this%20is%20extremely%20well%20done%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20immersing%20the%20reader%20in%20varieties%20of%20minority%20experience.%20In%20particular%2C%20there%20is%20the%20discomfiting%20scene%20of%20Alif%20and%20Tahira%20undergoing%20a%20derogatory%20interrogation%20while%20trying%20to%20rent%20a%20flat.%20At%20another%20time%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20told%20that%20Tahira%20dislikes%20the%20assumption%2C%20especially%20during%20Eid%2C%20that%20because%20she%20is%20Muslim%20and%20a%20woman%20she%20must%20be%20a%20great%20cook.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20this%20all%20we%20are%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asks%20Alif.%20%E2%80%9CBawarchis%3F%20Poetry-spouting%20fools%20with%20minced%20mutton%20coming%20out%20of%20our%20ears%2C%20thinking%20only%20of%20Allah%20and%20pining%20only%20for%20bahisht%20between%20mouthfuls%20of%20zafrani%20pulao%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20flip%20side%20of%20this%20is%20that%20there%20are%20stretches%20in%20which%20very%20little%20happens%20from%20a%20novelistic%20point%20of%20view.%20Instead%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%E2%80%99s%20Angel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20relies%20on%20creating%20empathy%20through%20well-rounded%20characters%20to%20propel%20itself%20forward%20by%20sinuous%20sentences.%20Because%20Alif%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20rather%20read%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Discovery%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20than%20discover%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20his%20complaisant%20nature%20isn%E2%80%99t%20entirely%20up%20to%20the%20job%20of%20sustaining%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20one%20stage%2C%20Alif%20politely%20informs%20his%20overly%20patriotic%20school%20principal%20while%20breaking%20into%20a%20sweat%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20a%20Muslim%20history%20of%20India%E2%80%A6try%20separating%20Muslims%20from%20Hindus%20in%20this%20way%20when%20you%20go%20into%20the%20past%20of%20this%20country%20and%20all%20you%20find%20are%20entanglements%E2%80%9D.%20Though%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20national%20destiny%20frightens%20him%2C%20he%20has%20little%20choice%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20moderate%20hopes%20and%20incremental%20changes%20that%20democratic%20statehood%20offers%20till%20they%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20substitute%20for%20it%2C%20which%20no%20one%20has%20so%20far%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20such%20ways%2C%20he%20personifies%20the%20novel%E2%80%99s%20title%2C%20taken%20from%20Walter%20Benjamin%E2%80%99s%20conception%20of%20the%20angel%20of%20history%2C%20whose%20face%20is%20turned%20towards%20the%20past%20with%20the%20wreckage%20of%20catastrophe%20piled%20at%20his%20feet.%20The%20angel%20wants%20