eries%20in%20the%20imagination%20of%20Indian%20nationhood.%20They%20are%20simply%20seen%20as%20territorial%20spatial%20units%20that%20need%20to%20be%20surveilled%20and%20securitised%20under%20military%20repression%20while%20its%20people%20can%20be%20treated%20as%20disposables%20for%20a%20misplaced%20national%20cause.%20Horrifying%20incidents%20in%20such%20spaces%20are%20thus%20viewed%20as%20normal%2C%20ignored%20or%20even%20legitimised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Manipur%2C%20like%20many%20other%20conflict%20zones%20in%20the%20north-east%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20lie%20on%20the%20extreme%20borders%20of%20the%20physical%20boundaries%20and%20memory%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20dehumanising%20violence%20is%20not%20a%20novelty.%20Their%20landscapes%20are%20littered%20with%20stories%20of%20egregious%20human%20rights%20violations%20including%20sexual%20violence%20perpetrated%20both%20by%20the%20state%20and%20the%20non-state%20actors.%20Nation-wide%20outrage%20is%20selectively%20evoked%2C%20if%20at%20all%2C%20only%20when%20the%20crimes%20are%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20non-state%20actors.%20Those%20committed%20by%20the%20state%20are%20wished%20away%2C%20defended%20and%20sometimes%20even%20celebrated.%20A%20large%20section%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20dominant%20media%20has%20allowed%20itself%20to%20be%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20of%20perpetuating%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20nation%20in%20which%20the%20people%20from%20these%20areas%20remain%20invisible%2C%20even%20deemed%20%E2%80%98the%20other%E2%80%99%20because%20they%20do%20not%20share%20the%20same%20sense%20of%20history.%20Attempts%20to%20mainstream%20them%20are%20not%20based%20on%20principles%20of%20diversity%20and%20accommodation%20but%20are%20rather%20treated%20as%20battles%20between%20the%20conquerors%20and%20the%20vanquished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22995%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM.png%20995w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19220406%2FScreenshot-2023-07-19-at-10.02.22-PM-300x159.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664029%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20from%20the%20viral%20video%20which%20shows%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20video%20that%20went%20viral%20is%20merely%20a%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg.%20More%20reports%20and%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20killings%2C%20displacements%20and%20the%20shocking%20territorialisation%20of%20Manipur%20along%20ethnic%20lines%20have%20now%20begun%20to%20tumble%20out.%20The%20scale%20of%20it%20would%20be%20much%20more%20horrifying%2C%20far%20more%20than%20what%20we%20have%20witnessed%20in%20Delhi%201984%2C%20Gujarat%202002%20and%20Muzaffarnagar%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20these%20previous%20cases%2C%20the%20rioters%20were%20given%20a%20free%20hand%20for%20a%20few%20days%20till%20the%20government%20began%20to%20act.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20mobs%20had%20a%20free%20for%20all%20situation%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%20because%20Manipur%20is%20imagined%20to%20be%20an%20appendage%20and%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20whole.%20The%20Meitei%20majority%20had%20been%20weaponised%20against%20the%20Kuki%20tribals%20%E2%80%93%20considered%20the%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98alien%E2%80%99%20even%20within%20this%20restive%20state%20%E2%80%93%20revealing%20that%20there%20exist%20more%20layers%20of%20exclusion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClashes%20have%20now%20abated%20but%20tensions%20persist%20%E2%80%93%20everything%20kept%20well%20under%20the%20garb%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe-cant-look-away-from-internet-shutdowns-in-manipur%5C%22%3Eimposed%20internet%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lack%20of%20mobile%20phone%20connectivity%20in%20many%20areas%20and%20a%20disinterested%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attention%20that%20this%20grave%20situation%20has%20received%20so%20far%20is%20too%20little%20and%20too%20disproportionate%20to%20the%20magnitude%20of%20what%20Manipur%20has%20witnessed.%20At%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20outrage%20is%20the%20chilling%20story%20of%20sexual%20assault.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20the%20sexual%20assault%20cases%20merit%20little%20or%20no%20attention%20in%20India%20is%20also%20crucial%20to%20understanding%20the%20deliberate%20silence%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20its%20media.%20It%20took%20digital%20images%20of%20sexually%20assaulted%20tribal%20Kuki%20women%20after%20the%20police%20literally%20fed%20them%20to%20the%20mob%20for%20the%20nation%20to%20sit%20up%20and%20take%20notice.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20even%20after%20the%20horrifying%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20nation%20appears%20to%20be%20divided%20between%20a%20sense%20of%20shame%20and%20whataboutery.%20More%20importantly%2C%20knowledge%20of%20such%20rapes%20and%20sexual%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20were%20not%20unknown%20before%20the%20video%20suddenly%20surfaced.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAllegations%20of%20women%20being%20violently%20assaulted%20were%20already%20in%20circulation%20after%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20May%204.%20Presumably%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Manipur%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20too%20knew%20about%20it%20since%20complaints%20and%20FIRs%20had%20been%20lodged%20in%20the%20police%20stations%20at%20least%20as%20early%20as%20May%2018.%20It%20is%20also%20common%20knowledge%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20are%20used%20as%20weapons%20of%20aggression%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20crisis%20that%20was%20unfolding%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20thus%20calls%20to%20question%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20collective%20conscience%20which%20requires%20disgusting%20images%20for%20incidents%20like%20these%20to%20wake%20us%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-a-complaint-on-the-may-4-assault-was-sent-to-ncw-but-the-complainants-never-got-a-reply%5C%22%3EA%20Complaint%20on%20the%20May%204%20Assault%20in%20Manipur%20Was%20Sent%20to%20NCW%20in%20June.%20But%20It%20Never%20Got%20a%20Reply%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERapes%20fall%20in%20the%20category%20of%20crimes%20that%20have%20been%20ignored%20and%20swept%20under%20the%20carpet%20through%20deliberate%20intent%20across%20India.%20For%20decades%20after%20independence%20and%20constitutional%20guarantees%20of%20equality%20and%20intolerance%20to%20injustices%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20have%20become%20markers%20of%20male%20machismo%20and%20collective%20triumph%20of%20communities%2C%20often%20with%20the%20tacit%20approval%20and%20encouragement%20by%20women.%20Equally%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20are%20wrongly%20deemed%20as%20repositories%20of%20the%20honour%20of%20the%20family%20or%20the%20community%20they%20belong%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20obsession%20with%20%E2%80%98purity%E2%80%99%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20has%20forbid%20a%20collective%20response%20against%20%E2%80%98defilement%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20bodies%20as%20part%20of%20male%20privilege%20or%20for%20revenge%20and%20humiliating%20the%20other.%20After%20the%20Delhi%20Nirbhaya%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20which%20sparked%20immediate%20nationwide%20outrage%20rape%20finally%20found%20some%20place%20in%20the%20mainstream%20conversations%20and%20national%20discourse.%20However%2C%20the%20empathy%20for%20the%20victim%20and%20outrage%20against%20such%20crimes%20continues%20to%20be%20coloured%20by%20prejudices%20of%20race%2C%20caste%2C%20class.%20It%20is%20rare%20for%20similar%20spontaneity%20and%20outrage%20to%20be%20evoked%20if%20the%20woman%20is%20a%20Dalit%2C%20a%20tribal%20or%20a%20Muslim.%20If%20at%20all%2C%20they%20make%20it%20to%20the%20news%20pages%2C%20it%20is%20left%20to%20the%20few%20feminists%20and%20liberals%20to%20speak%20for%20them.%20Unnao%2C%20Hathras%20and%20Kathua%20rapes%20and%20murders%20are%20cases%20in%20point.%20Sexual%20violence%20in%20conflict%20zones%20figures%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20this%20hierarchical%20pyramid.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F12110111%2F2020_10img02_Oct_2020_PTI02-10-2020_000244B-1200x600-1-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-509290%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMembers%20of%20various%20organisations%20during%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20death%20of%20a%2019-year-old%20Dalit%20woman%20who%20was%20gang-raped%20in%20Hathras%2C%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Friday%2C%20October%202%2C%202020.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESexual%20violence%20and%20conflict%20zones%20with%20disputed%20histories%20thus%20make%20a%20deadly%20combination%20engendering%20in%20the%20national%20conscience%20a%20wilful%20ignorance%20and%20forgetfulness%20of%20the%20troubles%2C%20strife%2C%20traumas%20and%20hopes%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20and%20fragile%20regions%20of%20the%20country.%20Throw%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20led%20government%E2%80%99s%20promotion%20of%20majoritarian%20politics%20of%20exclusion%20across%20the%20country%20and%20you%20have%20a%20virulent%20cocktail%20that%20can%20only%20result%20in%20a%20graver%20disaster.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20majoritarian%20push%20and%20his%20partisan%20role%20before%20and%20after%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20has%20brought%20alive%20the%20existing%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20faultlines%20in%20Manipur%20with%20domino%20effect%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20north-east.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Manipur%20crisis%20lays%20bare%20a%20national%20crisis%20of%20identity.%20There%20is%2C%20thus%2C%20a%20need%20to%20go%20beyond%20ordering%20independent%20probes%20and%20holding%20the%20government%20accountable%20for%20its%20calculated%20indifference%20to%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20blood-soaked%20battleground%2C%20dead%20bodies%2C%20brutalised%20people%2C%20sexually%20assaulted%20women%2C%20burnt%20and%20destroyed%20homes%2C%20displacements%20and%20rigid%20internal%20borders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20dire%20need%20for%20redefining%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20and%20re-envisioning%20it%20as%20a%20nation%20where%20the%20conflict%20zones%20that%20lie%20on%2