hat%20the%20State%20has%20no%20power%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20caste-based%20survey%2C%20in%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20is%20fashioned%20now%2C%20which%20would%20amount%20to%20a%20census%2C%20thus%20impinging%20upon%20the%20legislative%20power%20of%20the%20Union%20Parliament.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2018%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-lift-patna-hcs-stay-on-bihar-caste-census%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20lift%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20stay%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20census%20has%20become%20a%20major%20political%20concern%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20with%20opposition%20parties%20amping%20up%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20do%20the%20exercise%20on%20a%20national%20basis.%20It%20was%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20which%20first%20conducted%20a%20Socio-Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)%20in%202011-12%20but%20never%20released%20its%20data%20because%20of%20varied%20opinions%20about%20it%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20was%20more%20vocally%20expressed%20by%20different%20opposition%20parties%20after%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20implemented%20reservation%20for%20the%20Economically%20Weaker%20Classes%20(EWS)%2C%20which%20effectively%20gave%20a%20quota%20to%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cupper%20caste%E2%80%9D%20groups.%20The%20EWS%20reservation%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20anomaly%20in%20the%20caste-based%20affirmative%20action%20policy%20because%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fews-quota-a-stupefying-inversion-of-the-idea-of-equality%5C%22%3Ethe%20criteria%20was%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20was%20perceived%20by%20various%20parties%20as%20a%20move%