es%20from%20their%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20device%20is%20unique%20as%20other%20tools%20available%20in%20the%20market%20are%20mainly%20for%20foetal%20monitoring.%20However%2C%20we%20still%20recommend%20that%20women%20visit%20the%20hospital%20every%20month%2C%20where%20the%20doctor%20can%20review%20the%20monthly%20data%20and%20prescribe%20medication%20accordingly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20onboarded%2015%2C000%20healthcare%20workers%20and%202%2C500%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FmWsH9DVEptY%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20unique%20wearable%20for%20high-risk%20mothers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20this%20battery-operated%20device%20tracks%20their%20sleep%20cycle%2C%20calories%20burned%20(indicating%20nutritional%20deficiencies)%2C%20pulse%20rate%2C%20and%20steps.%20It%20also%20sends%20timely%20reminders%20for%20taking%20medicines.%20ASHA%20(Accredited%20Social%20Health%20Activist)%20workers%20can%20retrieve%20the%20recorded%20health%20data%20through%20Bluetooth%20and%20upload%20it%20to%20the%20cloud%2C%20where%20doctors%20can%20access%20it%20for%20review%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20explains%20a%20scenario%20where%20such%20devices%20are%20useful.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20high-risk%20mother%20has%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20doctors%20also%20consider%20her%20sleep%20pattern.%20If%20she%20isn%E2%80%99t%20getting%20proper%20sleep%2C%20it%20can%20contribute%20to%20increased%20blood%20pressure.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20doctor%20may%20prescribe%20different%20medications%20instead%20of%20a%20standard%20blood%20pressure%20tablet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20is%20collected%20weekly%20and%20reviewed%20by%20a%20doctor%20every%2015%20days.%20High-risk%20mothers%20are%20recommended%20to%20use%20the%20wearable%20device%20for%201%2C000%20days%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20from%20the%20fourth%20week%20of%20pregnancy%20until%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20second%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-150x79