o%20establish%20a%20recycling%20unit%20in%20Delhi.%20So%20I%20helped%20him%20set%20up%20the%20unit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20process%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319912%2Ftamil-nadu-father-son-duo-senthil-kumar-recycle-plastic-bottles-into-sustainable-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycling%20unit%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20Bhagyashree%20learnt%20a%20lot%20about%20plastic%20recycling.%20She%20went%20to%20various%20exhibitions%20to%20see%20the%20different%20recycling%20machines%20used%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMachines%20used%20in%20Germany%20and%20China%20would%20segregate%20the%20waste%2C%20but%20those%20machines%20could%20not%20process%20the%20type%20of%20waste%20we%20produced.%20So%20we%20had%20to%20segregate%20and%20clean%20the%20waste%20properly%20before%20using%20the%20machines%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2029-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20set%20up%20small%20segregation%20systems%20and%20tweaked%20the%20machinery%20to%20work%20according%20to%20the%20waste%20they%20needed%20to%20recycle%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20work%20with%20local%20recyclers%20and%20partnered%20with%20organisations%20like%20Mohan%20Meakins%2C%20Whirlpool%2C%20and%20Arvind%20Mills%20to%20establish%20efficient%20in-house%20plastic%20waste%20management%20systems.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20how%20to%20identify%20different%20kinds%20of%20plastic%2C%20its%20nature%2C%20qualities%20and%20recyclability%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20these%20learnings%20which%20eventually%20led%20to%20her%20startup%2C%20The%20Disposal%20Company%20(TDC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELove%20for%20skincare%20turned%20into%20a%20business%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-