35%20years%20old%2C%20Nimal%20left%20his%20job%20in%20Dubai%20to%20restore%20his%20hometown%E2%80%99s%20former%20prosperity.%20His%20first%20priority%20was%20reviving%20Peravurani%20lake%2C%20which%20could%20irrigate%20more%20than%206%2C000%20acres%20of%20farmland.%20The%20project%20required%20Rs%2032%20lakh%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20like-minded%20volunteers%2C%20he%20planted%2025%2C000%20saplings%20across%20the%20Kaveri%20delta%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20social%20media%20campaign%20%23BounceBackDelta%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20all%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20cyclone%20with%20clothes%2C%20groceries%2C%20household%20necessities%2C%20and%20money.%20The%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303262%2Fiit-roorkee-professor-technology-to-remove-arsenic-contamination-purify-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprojects%20taken%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20his%20team%20include%20the%20Miyawaki%20plantation%2C%20a%20mangrove%20forest%20plantation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20water%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20more%20than%2040%20lakh%20people%20have%20benefited%20from%20restored%20water%20bodies%2C%20which%20have%20helped%20them%20access%20fresh%20drinking%20water%2C%20irrigate%20agricultural%20land%2C%20and%20earn%20a%20livelihood.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20restored%20a%20total%20of%20118%20water%20bodies%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Babita%20Rajput%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20847px)%20100vw%2C%20847px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FBabita-1690465852.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22847%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Babita%20Rajput%20formed%20a%20group%20of%20200%20women%20in%20her%20village%20of%