n%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20giving%20birth%2C%20everyone%20tends%20to%20forget%20about%20the%20mother%20and%20focuses%20solely%20on%20the%20child.%20We%20want%20to%20prioritise%20the%20mother%20during%20the%20retreat.%20While%20we%20do%20cater%20to%20both%20the%20mother%20and%20child%2C%20we%20want%20to%20ensure%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%20needs%20are%20not%20overlooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nikita%2C%20who%20is%20a%20full-time%20blogger%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20the%20trips%20are%20planned%20for%20two%20nights%20and%20three%20days%2C%20where%20the%20children%20can%20have%20fun%20while%20the%20mothers%20unwind.%20So%20far%2C%20their%20curated%20experiences%20have%20included%20farm-to-table%20dining%2C%20a%20mud%20bath%20in%20Goa%2C%20a%20sound%20garden%20in%20Puducherry%2C%20a%20crocodile%20bank%2C%20cooking%20classes%2C%20and%20dining%20by%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20USP%20of%20their%20venture%20is%20that%20one%20of%20the%20two%20founders%20is%20always%20present%20on%20the%20trip.%20They%20personally%20visit%20and%20explore%20the%20locations%20beforehand%2C%20along%20with%20their%20families%2C%20before%20planning%20it%20for%20others.%20They%20mostly%20book%20homestays%20or%20boutique%20hotels%20with%20kitchenettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trips%20are%20usually%20priced%20around%20Rs%2020%2C000%E2%80%93Rs%2025%2C000%2C%20and%20each%20mother%20is%20given%20a%20separate%20room%20with%20her%20child%2Fchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20816px)%20100vw%2C%20816px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel3-1690375408.jpg%20816w%2C%20https%3A%2