joined%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20single%20mothers%20on%20the%20trips.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20supportive%20community%20of%20like-minded%20mothers%2C%20providing%20a%20non-judgemental%20space.%20Motherhood%20brings%20changes%20to%20all%20of%20us%2C%20and%20sometimes%20we%20may%20forget%20to%20prioritise%20ourselves.%20Many%20moms%20lose%20confidence%20in%20travelling%20alone%20with%20their%20kids.%20We%20want%20mothers%20to%20realise%20that%20they%20can%20still%20travel%2C%20albeit%20differently%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nikita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nikita%20and%20Saakshi%2C%20some%20of%20the%20mothers%20who%20went%20on%20their%20trips%20have%20bonded%20so%20well%20that%20they%20now%20meet%20up%20regularly.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20all%20had%20similar%20experiences.%20We%20just%20need%20someone%20to%20talk%20to%20who%20has%20been%20through%20the%20same.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20everyone%20bonds%20so%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikita%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThey%20want%20mothers%20across%20the%20country%20to%20travel%20with%20their%20children.%20%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201088px)%20100vw%2C%201088px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406.jpg%201088w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel4-1690375406-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325206%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20duo%20has%20planned%2020%20trips%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20few%20tweaks%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20manageable%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20to%20places%20which%20aren%E2%80%99t%20considered%20%E2%80%98kid-friendly%E2%80%99%20like%20Reunion%20Island%2C%20Morocco%20and%20Egypt.%20My%20daughter%20enjoyed%20it.%20Kids%20will%20always%20find%20a%20way%20to%20entertain%20themselves.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20always%20go%20to%20zoos%20or%20parks.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20the%20sensory%20experience%20of%20being%20in%20a%20new%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20I%20travelled%20solo%2C%20then%20with%20my%20husband%20whose%20interests%20are%20very%20different.%20Now%20my%20children%E2%80%99s%20interests%20are%20different.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20needs%20as%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20manage%20their%20interests%20themselves.%20So%20you%20have%20to%20do%20it%20for%20them.%20But%20in%20this%20process%2C%20you%20get%20to%20see%20the%20world%20through%20their%20eyes%2C%20which%20is%20simply%20amazing.%20It%E2%80%99s%20different%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20exchange%20it%20for%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Nikita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302712%2Fpuducherry-social-worker-helps-tribal-children-study-become-engineers-teachers-udhavi-karangal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20let%20motherhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20become%20a%20barrier%20in%20pursuing%20your%20dreams.%20Believe%20in%20yourself%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20make%20yourself%20a%20priority.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20anyone%20tell%20yo