%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20needed%20a%20more%20stimulating%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20such%20a%20bare%2C%20unfurnished%20room%2C%20%5Bthey%5D%20were%20desperate%20for%E2%80%A6activities%20for%20their%20hands%2C%20and%20that%20this%20deprivation%20was%20contributing%20to%20their%20condition%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20observation%20was%20among%20the%20first%20seeds%20sowed%20for%20what%20is%20now%20known%20as%20the%20Montessori%20method%2C%20which%2C%20over%20a%20century%20later%2C%20has%20spread%20far%20and%20wide%20across%20the%20world%20and%20to%20children%20across%20the%20spectrum.%20It%20encourages%20a%20%E2%80%98different%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98informal%E2%80%99%20way%20of%20learning.%20Though%20acknowledged%20to%20have%20both%20pros%20and%20cons%2C%20Dr%20Montessori%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20pioneered%20early%20childhood%20education%20in%20a%20way%20that%20helps%20children%20develop%20their%20own%20pace%20and%20learning%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20820px)%20100vw%2C%20820px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Maria%20Montessori%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985.jpg%20820w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985-500x282.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985-768x433.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985-150x85.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325135%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhen%20Maria%20Montessori%20began%20her%20work%2C%20it%20was%20for%20disabled%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJo%20Chopra-McGowan%2C%20who%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F178695%2Fbengaluru-tactile-books-graphics-education-disability-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20towards%20the%20inclusion%20of%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20disabilities%20for%20over%2030%20years%2C%20says%20that%20you%20will%20often%20find%20that%20inclusive%20practices%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20uplift%20a%20certain%20group%20%E2%80%94%20they%E2%80%99re%20for%20society%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJo%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Latika%20(previously%20Latika%20Roy%20Foundation%2C%20or%20LRF)%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20has%2C%20since%201994%2C%20worked%20with%20thousands%20of%20children%20and%20adults%20with%20intellectual%20and%20physical%20disabilities%20to%20help%20them%20mainstream%20in%20society.%20Among%20their%20key%20projects%20is%20to%20work%20with%20disabled%20children%20in%20their%20early%20years%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccatch%20them%20young%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20one%20of%20their%20programmes%20says.%20This%20inclusion%20centres%20around%20their%20education%2C%20but%20also%20looks%20to%20integrate%20them%20into%20the%20mainstream%20as%20a%20whole%20and%20for%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Maria%20Montessori%20began%20her%20work%2C%20it%20was%20for%20disabled%20children.%20But%20parents%20soon%20realised%20that%20this%20could%20work%20for%20other%20children%20too.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%E2%80%99re%20always%20telling%20people%2C%20that%20when%20you%20target%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20child%20in%20the%20room%2C%20your%20whole%20classroom%20will%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Everybody%20is%20welcome%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatika%E2%80%99s%20work%20with%20disabled%20children%20began%20when%20Jo%20and%20her%20husband%20Ravi%20adopted%20Moy%20Moy%2C%20who%20also%20lived%20with%20a%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20as%20just%20an%20inclusive%20play%20centre%20where%20children%20of%20all%20kinds%20could%20come%20after%20school%20and%20engage%20in%20fun%20activities.%20The%20only%20rules%20were%20that%20you%20play%20fair%20and%20welcome%20everybody%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jo%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20lots%20of%20kids%20with%20disabilities%20coming%20in%20naturally%3B%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20active%20effort%20on%20our%20part%2C%20but%20they%20came%20because%20of%20the%20inclusive%20environment%20we%E2%80%99d%20built.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FClDz_IEOdMY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FClDz_IEOdMY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22n